==English==

===Alternative forms===
* [[evangelise]] ''(not US)

===Verb===
{{en-verb|evangeliz|ing}}

* Activity of an occasional religious preacher, sometimes itinerant and often preaching at meetings in the open air
* The preaching or promulgation of the gospel; the work of an [[evangelist]]. 
* Religious missionary, purpose, or activity. 
* The act of winning or revival of personal commitments to Christ. 


